promptTemplate:
[TASK] {{taskId}}
action: refactor
branch: {{branch}}
files: {{files}}
description: {{description}}
{{#reason}}
Reason:
{{reason}}
{{/reason}}
{{#constraints}}
Constraints:
{{constraints}}
{{/constraints}}
---
Refactor the code as described. Ensure no behavior changes unless specified.
Run tests before committing.
Work on the specified branch. When done, commit and push the branch (NOT main).
Then use report_task_result with the branch name and commit hash.
